the gifcycle shows the steps 

![topview_alters_confgiuration_data](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/278728/185961405-6385be89-ba37-4ec5-9e6c-6397bb5a5e7c.gif)

For the config editor only the  "llcrnrlon", "llcrnrlat", "urcrnrlon", "urcrnrlat" should be used and only this should be saved for the map entry.

**[Original report](https://bitbucket.org/wxmetvis/mss/issue/208) by Andreas Hilboll (Bitbucket: [andreas-h](https://bitbucket.org/andreas-h), GitHub: [andreas-h](https://github.com/andreas-h)).**

